Firstly run the aplication i.e. server side on the server's PC.
At client side start from the Home Page.If you are new user you'll have to sign up first .
At login time if you forgot the password then you can get your password on your registered email id by pressing forgot password button.
after login you will get a jFrame that will show a button "click" and a jTable and "choose" button.Here clicking "click" button will show all the
the PC's IP address, that will be in active mode i.e. connected to LAN and have running server side application(very small  java executable file).
From the jTable you can select any IP address and get the control of that computer.
